<h2><span id="1._Nc3_-_Van_Geet_Opening">1. Nc3 - Van Geet Opening</span></h2>
<p>A rarely played opening. Allows for a variety of transpositions and some independent lines.  Black's best response is to threaten to chase the White knight at c3 away with 1... d5.  1... e5 allows White to transpose into a Vienna game.
</p>
